processDocumentation.samplingDescription:
This activity originates from literature data, based on robust modelling, for the production of methanol from steam methane reforming published in 2017. The material and energy inputs reflect well the production technology and not expected to change significantly over time or geography.

References;
Santos, S. O., Collodi, G., Azzaro, G., & Ferrari, N. (2017). Techno-economic evaluation of Hyco plant integrated to ammonia/urea or methanol production with CCS. IEAGHG.
